reviewText: The dvd took a long time to arrive and it was not made for our dvd player, it was scratched and I feel like I got a bad deal. Not happy with this purchase. My daughter does not watch it because she can't get it to play properly. Please send me a replacement please.
It dosent play in a dvd player or car dvd player. Not happy with my purchase because my daughter loves this TV show and the dvd was a waste of money. It wouldn't play!!!
